talletBody\" style=\"background:transparent;\" class=\"portalletBody purplePortalletBody\"><p>No courses were found.</p><div style=\"clear:both;overflow:hidden;\"></div></div><div id=\"mySections_portallet_portalletFooter\" class=\"portalletFooter\"><div id=\"mySections_portallet_portalletFooterLeft\" class=\"portalletFooterLeft purplePortalletFooterLeft\"></div><div id=\"mySections_portallet_portalletFooterRight\" class=\"portalletFooterRight purplePortalletFooterRight\"></div><div id=\"mySections_portallet_portalletFooterBorder\" class=\"portalletFooterBorder purplePortalletFooterBorder\"></div></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t<td width=\"3%\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n\t</tr>\r\n\t<tr>\r\n\t\t<td colspan=\"5\"><h2 class=\"Paragraph SCXW100780986 BCX0\" role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"1\" paraid=\"635781132\" paraeid=\"{c97a3013-484d-4e50-9e3f-b4dc2e447a91}{210}\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"></strong></span></h2><h1><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">Welcome to the 2025-2026 School Year!</span></h1><div><div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW143356700 BCX0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><br/></div><div></div></div><span><br/></span><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110033593 BCX0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW110033593 BCX0\" paraid=\"1568660695\" paraeid=\"{f979011b-f30e-48cc-861c-47b5306c9d09}{11}\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;\">Learning Coach Support</span></p></div><br/><div><p style=\"background-color: #ffffff; margin: 0in; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"background: white; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 19px; margin-top: 8px;\"><strong>Registration</strong><br/>Registration for the winter 2026 Learning Coach Support live webinars is now open! Click <a href=\"https://app.smartsheet.com/b/publish?EQBCT=c7d121c5fbcb4ca4a08350dd96fe0116\" target=\"_blank\" id=\"OWAf50fea3f-31e1-f2d6-072f-1225008579b5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-auth=\"NotApplicable\" style=\"color: #003399;\">here</a> to check out our schedule and dive into the amazing Learning Coach Community. Don't forget&#160;<a href=\"/library/default.aspx?lineage=%2fHome%2fLearning+Coach+Central%2f&category=Learning+Coach+Central\" target=\"_blank\" id=\"OWA4446472a-7597-9b38-af73-e631d537a60b\" class=\"OWAAutoLink\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-auth=\"NotApplicable\" style=\"color: #003399;\">Learning Coach Central</a>&#160;is your go-to spot for&#160;<a href=\"https://app.smartsheet.com/b/publish?EQBCT=e0be8e625742446eae9368ba9ae86339\" target=\"_blank\">webinar recordings</a>&#160;and new resources. See you there!<br/><br/><strong>We'd Love Your Feedback</strong><br/>Help us shape the future of the Learning Coach experience! Join our virtual Learning Coach Focus Group and share your experiences and feedback with our team. To join, complete this quick <a href=\"https://forms.office.com/pages/responsepage.aspx?id=1zTEjNCX00e1xRT-DjPjS4Wpz67v269Isld0L0uzq5JUMU5CVE5NUjBCRFIyQUFNNldSUVdYTVE4Mi4u&fbclid=IwY2xjawQFozFleHRuA2FlbQIxMABicmlkETJYRGptNTRxNVFXM3pJODFCc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQQMjIyMDM5MTc4ODIwMDg5MgABHv1Eo_Rd5e0OXJ4nP7r5HHC6xnqwAGNOCwwtBmFZj-kG3dvcPawnb2ku4YQt_aem_LWZ_q9XstKKcJiFT2MAaIg&route=shorturl\" target=\"_blank\">interest survey.</a></p><h3>Global Clubs & Activities<br/><img alt=\"\" src=\"/content/media/4626651-272025-51648-PM-1172863941.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"324\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;\"/></h3><strong></strong>There is still time to join a Global Club or Activity! Enrollment will remain open through April 15, 2026. Caretakers can sign-up students from their homepage and can check out the&#160;<a href=\"https://www.connectionsclubsandactivities.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Global Clubs & Activities website</a>&#160;for more information and instructions. All clubs are optional, have no impact on grades, and are 100% virtual and free.<br/><br/></div><h3>Peer Tutor</h3><div></div><p>Peer Tutoring is back for the spring 2026 semester and will be held on Monday, Tuesday, and Wednesday afternoons between 2:00 p.m. and 5:00 p.m. ET. If any of your students need help in their math coursework and are taking middle school (grades 6-8) math, Pre-algebra or Algebra Readiness, Algebra I, and Geometry, they are welcome to drop into our peer tutoring LiveLesson room to receive help from dedicated, qualified, and knowledgeable high school Connections Academy students.<br style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"/><br style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"/><strong style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">New this year</strong>: In order for students to enter the peer tutoring room, their parents/Caretakers must go to the Clubs and Activities Data View and select \"Peer Tutoring\" to sign up. Details on how to complete this process can be found on the&#160;<a href=\"https://www.connectionsclubsandactivities.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #003399; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Clubs and Activities Website</a>. If families or students have any questions, they should WebMail the Peer Tutoring Lead, Mr. Matthew Caillet at this&#160;<a href=\"/webmail?hideHeader=true/#/composemessage?idRecipient=5981400&subject=Questions%20about%20Peer%20Tutor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #003399; font-size: 14px;\">link</a>. Teachers/administrators/counselors can e-mail Mr. Caillet at&#160;<a href=\"mailto:mdcaillet@pearsoneducator.com\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #003399; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">mdcaillet@pearsoneducator.com</a>.</p><div><br/></div><h2><span>The Help Desk</span></h2><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 16pt;\"><span><strong style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"></strong></span></strong><span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 16pt;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"></strong></strong><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"></strong></strong></span><h2 style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"/content/media/2015125-8132020-10748-PM-1602876347.png\" width=\"161\" height=\"200\" style=\"font-size: medium; font-weight: 400; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;\"/><strong><br/></strong></span></h2><p class=\"news\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"></span></p><span>Connections Academy School Leaders, Teachers, and School Staff: The information below is for you to get the help and support you need as quickly as possible.<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"></span></span><p><span>For password reset assistance:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"/forgot.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Pearson Online Classroom password reset</a><a href=\"https://e23.ultipro.com/login.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">UKG (UltiPro) Log In</a>: Select \"Forgot your Password?\"</span></li><li><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://www.concursolutions.com/profile/send_password_hint.asp\" target=\"_blank\">Concur Forgot Password</a></span></li><li><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://support.connexus.com/s/\" target=\"_blank\">Online Help</a>: Enter \"password\" in the search to obtain further access-related support.</span></li></ul>*Please note: not all schools use these services.<p class=\"Paragraph SCXW213419878 BCX0\" paraid=\"1097657176\" paraeid=\"{f8f6e94e-eb55-4865-984f-36ebfd85f475}{134}\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">To contact Pearson Virtual Schools for help or support:</span></p>Please call 855-330-INFO (4636). Help Desk representatives are available to help with technical issues, Pearson Online Classroom, School Year Cycle events, and guidance on addressing questions from families. <br/>This Help Desk phone number should not be shared with Learning Coaches, Caretakers, students, or other external parties. <br/><br/>Follow the prompts to be routed to the School Technical Support or School Support Team. <strong>Both teams are available 8:00 a.m. to 6:00 p.m. ET Monday-Friday except during special hours.&#160;</strong>Note: The School Support Help Desk will be closed on Fridays for team meetings from 3:25 p.m. to 4:00 p.m. ET. Please leave a message and your call will be returned as soon as possible. Connections Academy families<span> should call 800-382-6010 and listen to the prompts to address their specific needs.<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><br class=\"SCXW213419878 BCX0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; white-space: pre !important;\"/></span><br/>District Partner School Leaders, teachers and staff may call the Client Services team at 800-848-9500 for help or support. District Partner families should call 888-679-7740 for technical assistance.</span><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW213419878 BCX0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\"></div><strong>For questions relating to Human Resources</strong><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW213419878 BCX0\" paraid=\"1919739514\" paraeid=\"{2f3d63db-85bd-4b6b-bc2d-9a950b64e85e}{115}\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext;\">New hires: Your Hiring Manager is your point of contact for onboarding credentials.</span></p>Current school employees: Contact your dedicated HR support team at: {Your school <span style=\"-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">acronym}HR@pearson.com</span>. Student Academic Services teams: Teaching Services, LiveSpeech, and Tutoring Services, please contact <span style=\"-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">SASHR@pearson.com</span>.<br class=\"SCXW213419878 BCX0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; white-space: pre !important;\"/>Pearson Virtual Schools employees:<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> Please log into myCloud and seek assistance through myHelp.<br/><br/><br/><p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"></span><br/><br/></span></p><div style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\"><strong><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/content/media/2015125-8132020-125946-PM-853554975.png\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; width: 200px; height: 200px;\"/></strong></strong></div><strong></strong><br/><map id=\"rade_img_map_1597338404896\" name=\"rade_img_map_1597338404896\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><area shape=\"RECT\" coords=\"81,79,117,122\" href=\"http:\"/></map><strong style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"></strong></span></div></td>\r\n\t</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"validationAlert\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n\r\n</div><script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n//<![CDATA[\r\nSys.WebForms.PageRequestManager._initialize('scriptManager', 'ctl00', [], [], [], 90, '');\r\n//]]>\r\n</script>\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"webuserWhenPageFirstLoaded\" id=\"webuserWhenPageFirstLoaded\" value=\"6141903\" />\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n//<![CDATA[\r\nvar Page_ValidationSummaries =  new Array(document.getElementById(\"validationAlert\"));\r\n//]]>\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n//<![CDATA[\r\nvar validationAlert = document.all ? document.all[\"validationAlert\"] : document.getElementById(\"validationAlert\");\r\nvalidationAlert.headertext = \"Some of the data you are trying to submit is incomplete or contains an error. Please correct the problem and try again.\";\r\nvalidationAlert.showmessagebox = \"True\";\r\nvalidationAlert.showsummary = \"False\";\r\nvalidationAlert.displaymode = \"List\";\r\n//]]>\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n//<![CDATA[\r\n if(document.forms[0] != undefined) document.forms[0].action = document.forms[0].action.replace('\\'','%27');\r\n(function(id) {\r\n    var e = document.getElementById(id);\r\n    if (e) {\r\n        e.dispose = function() {\r\n            Array.remove(Page_ValidationSummaries, document.getElementById(id));\r\n        }\r\n        e = null;\r\n    }\r\n})('validationAlert');\r\n//]]>\r\n</script>\r\n</form>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!-- End of pageContentContainer -->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"rightSideLinks\" style=\"display: none\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr valign=\"